title: List of Kentucky Wildcats starting quarterbacks
data: This is a year-by-year list of every Kentucky Wildcats football team quarterback and the years they participated on the Kentucky Wildcats football team. The following players were the predominant quarterbacks for the Wildcats each season after the establishment of the Southeastern Conference. The following players were the predominant quarterbacks for the Wildcats each season after the establishment of the Southern Conference until the establishment of the Southeastern Conference. The following players were the predominant quarterbacks for the Wildcats each season after the establishment of the Southern Intercollegiate Athletic Association until the establishment of the Southern Conference.
